<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>brahmakapālē bhōjanamayuktamiti vā vicāryya pūrnnēṁ<unclear>du</unclear>nibhaṁ rājatama<supplied reason="omitted">ma</supplied> laṁ prādātsa palla <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> bhīmanāthāya [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] A<unclear>di</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kubhṛdaśanirayaṁ śanivārē <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> yetra bhīmēśāya Uppōjāmagrāmē krī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tvādāddrāṣṭrakūṭamācaṁdrarkkaṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] sa tu guddavādiviṣayē kroppalligrāmarāṣṭrakūṭaṁ krītvā prādādācaṁdrārkkaṁ viṁśati<unclear>śi</unclear>vayōgināṁ ca nityaṁ bhōktuṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] nidhi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> gaganēṁdvyātē śākābdavarggē sucaraṇaguṇamā
<lb n="3" break="no"/><unclear>nī</unclear> pallavēśasya vutraḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Akṛśadaśasudīpaṁ dīpramācaṁdratāraṁ tridaśapatimahimnē bhīmanāthāya bhaktyā [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4*] śākābdā<unclear>nāṁ</unclear> pramānē nidhinayanaviyaccaṁdragē ca <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> nāmnā paṁkajavallī jaga<unclear>da</unclear>bhivinutā kalpavallī
<lb n="4" break="no"/>va lōkē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> bhīmēśāya pradīpaṁ tribhuvanavibhavē kalpitākhaṇḍavarttiṁ dākṣārāmādhipāyadadadamalamatiḥ pallavēśapriyē<unclear>ya</unclear>ṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 5*] sva(ta)māturumanaṁgāyāṁ sunāmnā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> valyalaṁ dīpaṁ bhīmēsvarāyādādakhaṇḍaṁ punyavridya<unclear>rtthaṁ</unclear> [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 6*]
</p>

